---
title: Join an Action Group
description: Join an action group to work collaboratively to end homelessness in Manchester
layout: default.hbs
permalink: false
appName: joinActionGroup
sectionName: charter
---

<div class="block">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="h1 block__header">Manchester Homelessness Charter</h1>
    <h2 class="h2 block__sub-header">Join an Action Group</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block block--breadcrumbs">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="https://streetsupport.net/">Home</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/">Charter</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item">Join an Action Group</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="block__content">
      <h2 class="h2">What is an action group?</h2>
      <p>Eight action groups have been created as a result of speaking to people experiencing homeless and organisations which are working hard to overcome their challenges. Each action group will concentrate on one key issue, such as mental health, employment or emergency accommodation.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Why join an action group?</h2>
      <p>By joining an action group you’ll have the opportunity to make use of your skills and experience, build strong networks with people who have the same dedication to ending homelessness, and be part of a team which leads the way in tackling key issues.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">What does it involve?</h2>
      <p>Once you have selected an action group you feel will benefit from your experience, you will be contacted by the group Chairperson to discuss details. The Chairperson will be responsible for keeping the group focussed and organising meetings. Each group will decide themselves how to work effectively, but we expect each group to meet no more than once a month.</p>

      <div class="pledge js-pledge">
        {{> loading-anim }}
        <h2 class="h2">Join an Action Group</h2>

        <div class="step">
          <ol class="step__list">
            <li class="step__item" data-bind="css: { active: section1.isActive() }"><a href="#" data-bind="click: setSection1Active">1</a></li>
            <li class="step__item" data-bind="css: { active: section2.isActive() }">2</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <form action="" class="pledge-form js-pledge-form">
          <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--1" data-bind="css: { active: section1.isActive() }">
            <p>Please select the action group you are interested in joining:</p>
            <div class="action-select">
              <ul class="action-select__list" data-bind="foreach: actionGroups">
                <li class="action-select__item" data-bind="click: selectActionGroup">
                  <span class="action-select__logo">
                    Logo
                  </span>
                  <span class="action-select__summary">
                    <h3 class="h3 action-select__name" data-bind="text: name"></h3>
                    <p class="action-select__description" data-bind="text: synopsis"></p>
                  </span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>If there is an issue not listed here, which you think worthy of an action group please email your suggestions to <a href="mailto:actiongroups@streetsupport.net">actiongroups@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--2" data-bind="css: { active: section2.isActive() }">
            <div data-bind="with: selectedActionGroup">
              <ul class="action-select__list">
                <li class="action-select__item">
                  <span class="action-select__logo">
                    Logo
                  </span>
                  <span class="action-select__summary">
                    <h3 class="h3 action-select__name" data-bind="text: name"></h3>
                    <p data-bind="text: synopsis"></p>
                  </span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p data-bind="text: description"></p>
            </div>
            <div data-bind="with: formModel">
              <h2 class="h2">Register your interest</h2>

              <span>We’d love to know more about you. How can you contribute to this action group? Do you have any super powers, special skills or relevant experience? How much time can you commit to the action group? Do you have any questions you’d like us to answer? (The chairperson of this group will be in touch with more information.)</span>
              <textarea style="margin-top: 2rem;" class="pledge-form__textarea" id="pledge" name="pledge" data-bind="textInput: pledge"></textarea>

              <ul class="pledge-form__list">

                <li class="pledge-form__item">
                  <label class="pledge-form__label" for="firstName">First Name *</label>
                  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name *" data-bind="textInput: firstName"></input>
                </li>
                <li class="pledge-form__item">
                  <label class="pledge-form__label" for="lastName">Last Name *</label>
                  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name *" data-bind="textInput: lastName"></input>
                </li>
                <li class="pledge-form__item">
                  <label class="pledge-form__label" for="organisation">Organisation/Business Name (if applicable)</label>
                  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="organisation" name="organisation" placeholder="Organisation Name" data-bind="textInput: organisation"></input>
                </li>
                <li class="pledge-form__item">
                  <label class="pledge-form__label" for="email">Email * <span style="display: block; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 14px">(Street Support will never share your email with a 3rd party.)</span></label>
                  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" data-bind="textInput: email"></input>
                </li>
                <li class="pledge-form__item">
                  <label class="pledge-form__label pledge-form__label--large" for="subscribe">Select to receive email updates from Street Support about homelessness and the Charter</label>
                  <input class="pledge-form__checkbox" type="checkbox" name="subscribe" data-bind="checked: isOptedIn">
                </li>
              </ul>

              <button class="btn pledge-form__btn" data-bind="click: $parent.submitPledge">Register my interest</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>

        <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--3" data-bind="css: { active: section3.isActive() }">
          <h2 class="h2">Thank you for your interest</h2>
          <p>Thank you for offering to be part of this action group. The chairperson for this group will be in touch with more information.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

